    "description": "可怕的僵尸瘟疫蔓延全球，唯一的治愈方法就是酒精。<br>在强烈的宿醉保护下，人类不惜一切代价夺回世界，或者只是享受生活，直到它终结。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2399850/extras/3f83d9c29cdebcd1a03c1fbd5e7b6958.poster.avif?t=1717499081\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2399850/extras/3f83d9c29cdebcd1a03c1fbd5e7b6958.webm?t=1717499081\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2399850/extras/3f83d9c29cdebcd1a03c1fbd5e7b6958.mp4?t=1717499081\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>想知道一切是从哪里开始的，以及是否是一款适合与朋友一起玩的有趣游戏吗？<br><br>试试《醉醺或死2：序章》。<br><br>您将获得：<br><br>对《醉醺或死》世界的介绍，<br>多个游戏内地点，<br>多种类型的武器，<br>《醉醺或死2：序章》是《醉醺或死2》的入门演示，这是一款面向最多四名玩家（合作）的基于任务的虚拟现实冒险游戏，提供了许多机会，可以在战斗之间出去、购物、聊天和喝酒。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2399850/extras/130a900f2b2c719af636afd8b6103b31.poster.avif?t=1717499081\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2399850/extras/130a900f2b2c719af636afd8b6103b31.webm?t=1717499081\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2399850/extras/130a900f2b2c719af636afd8b6103b31.mp4?t=1717499081\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>《醉醺或死2》的序章，您将在其中了解到主游戏中发生了什么事的简要历史。在序章中，玩家将尝试《醉醺或死2》宇宙的新有趣机制，例如：炮塔射击、新类型的僵尸、保卫小屋免受僵尸袭击以及尝试在谷物收割机上除掉僵尸。",
